text:
BINGO! Michelle Malkin has a more accurate name for ‘sanctuary cities’ [video] Posted at 12:34 pm on February 22, 2017 by Doug P. 
There’s been plenty of debate over “sanctuary cities” lately, but Michelle Malkin has a better name: "We have to stop calling these places 'sanctuary' cities. They're outlaw cities."– @michellemalkin pic.twitter.com/5Nyey6Y7GX 
— FOX & friends (@foxandfriends) February 22, 2017 
Mayors and supporters of sanctuary outlaw cities would take offense, but it is what it is: @michellemalkin just called sanctuary cities what they really are, outlaw cities. Good call 
— Daniel Mckee (@danielmckee3) February 22, 2017 Calling them what they are! SANCTUARY cities = OUTLAW cities! https://t.co/hBUuOBTwzZ 
— Carol Magee (@CarolMagee18) February 22, 2017 @foxandfriends @michellemalkin This again is the culture Obama created, by not enforcing the law. 
— Veteran Dan (@danecover1) February 22, 2017 @danielmckee3 @michellemalkin 80% of Americans are against them too. 
— Trevor Olson (@Tsveno) February 22, 2017 Trending
